{
  "stem": "17606.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 191.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they were sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those-- if the River Bug could talk, hundreds of hundreds and maybe of thousands were drowned over there, which the subbers were shotting at them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stayed in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, my friends on Betar came to me not long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They say few days after I came back, it was known that I am-- I am back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came to me and told me, you know, the Betar still is in existence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are illegal, but we still meet, and those who belonged to the former-- to the-- to the Corridor, what we call the [HEBREW] are meeting.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are a member of the Corridor, so you're welcome to join us back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made an appointment for two days later, and I was taken by Paul Frankel who was in charge of the-- of the [HEBREW] Corridor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-called [SPEAKING HEBREW], if you understand Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was taken to a house in the strictly Jewish neighborhood, [INAUDIBLE] 23.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went into that house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From that house, we went into a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how is it-- usually it's a [HEBREW] and a--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the top of the-- the--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The attic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is, through that attic, we went into another attic for another building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went through about two floors, and went in through a broken wall to another building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Went up to the attic, then to another three attics, and then we went down--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and I was taken down to a arsenal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my eyes didn't want to believe what was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Heavy machine guns.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Grenades.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rifles.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Guns.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sables.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bayonets.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You name it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to Paul, Paul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How, from where?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
